description:

Kohya GUI, 56 Images, 100 per.

You are responsible for the images created by you. Unethical usage of this LORA is prohibited.

I strongly advise against uploading any NSFW generated by this model. I warmly welcome you to communicate with me here on how to improve the working method to make the model more realistic. I am currently considering how to generate a better version 2.0. If you have any suggestions, such as choosing different base models, training with more images, increasing the number of training steps, or changing the training size to achieve a more realistic overall effect, please feel free to leave a comment below.

I advice to put this model weight between 0.3 and 0.45 for best results, i also advice to use DMP++ Sampling methods and with a CFG of 7-8 or similar.

some keywords you might want to know about the trained model are:

sexy pose, posing for a photo, tiny body, leopard print lingerie, stocking, nurse lingerie, beautifull hands. in any case try to always put the keyword lingerie somewhere, best results with "wearing lingerie in a sexy pose".

you might also want to try to write "making a photo of herself" or "making a selfie" but that doesn't always work.

follow my twitter page to be updated for new models and new versions, my nickname is Antonio_Riolo87. feel free to twit me for model requests!!

You can look at the images posted for example prompts, you might see Yui_v2 lora, it's a model i made, you can find it here: https://civitai.com/models/28118/yui-asian-sexy-girl

Enjoy!
